Elemental being

POISON ARCHER Poison Shot
every attack poison the target dealing 2 4 6 8 pure damage per 0.5 second plus 15% of the Skeleton Archer damage and reducing healing
effect by 10% and last 3 second, also 40% 50% 60% 70% of the poison archer damage is Pure

ICE ARCHER Ice Shot
the Archer got 25% chance to Slow the target movementspeed by 6% 7% 8% 9% and attackspeed by 4 6 8 10 also dealing 7 14 21 28 
physical damage plus 25% of the Skeleton Archer damage after the duration ends, if the skeleton archer refresh the duration of Ice Shot,
it will get 10% increase damage every time up to 50% max damage

FIRE ARCHER Molten Heart
the fire archer has 15% 18% 21% 24% chance to deal 140% 160% 180% 200%, melting the armor and reducing it by 1 2 3 4 that last 4 second
and if the skeleton crit again he will refresh the duration and increase the armor lost by 1 up to 2 3 4 5 max armor lost

LIGHTNING ARCHER Lightning Core
Change the Archer attack to become a Chain Lightning that bounce to 3 target max, dealing 3 5 7 9 bonus magical damage on hit and
reducing their magic resist by 4% 6% 8% 10% for 3 second, also change the archer attack damage to be magical attack damage and having
0.15 0.20 0.25 0.30 reduce base attack time as well

