ULTIMATE R
Death Touch
casting Death Touch on any Summon will give it to all of them increasing damage,attack speed,armor and magic resist or if casted on 
enemys they will suffer insane damage per second losing magic resist,attack speed and reducing all type of damage they do

IF CAST ON ENEMY
damage per second 25 50 75 plus 30% 40% 50% of int -damage type magical-
